  "id": "MGASA-2022-0231",
  "summary": "Updated golang packages fix security vulnerability",
  "details": "crypto/tls: session tickets lack random ticket_age_add. Session tickets\ngenerated by crypto/tls did not contain a randomly generated\nticket_age_add. This allows an attacker that can observe TLS handshakes to\ncorrelate successive connections by comparing ticket ages during session\nresumption. (CVE-2022-30629)\n",
